descriptionHtml:
Fennec File Manager — explorer for managing files on any storages, ROOT, SAF, SD card, USB, SMB, FTP, FTPS, SFTP. Compress/extract archives, analyze files.

* Supports various types of files, listen to music, see photos in one application!
* Archive support: Compress/unpacking ZIP, 7z, TAR, GZip, BZip2, only unpacking: RAR, CPIO, ISO, ARJ, CAB, DEB, RPM.

* Data encryption: You can encrypt files using AES 256 bit encryption.
* Network: Access to files via SMB, FTP, FTPS, SFTP. SMB 2 is supported.
* ROOT Explorer: Allows you to manage system files and folders on rooted devices.
* Memory analyzer: Shows all information about the storage used and possible ways to clear the memory. Use the analyzer to clean large, duplicate files!
* Bookmarks and history of open files: Allows you to quickly find files that you often work with.
* Clipboard: Allows you to select multiple files or folders from multiple media and directories at once!
* Recycle Bin: Delete files safely, with the possibility of recovery.
* Dark theme: Reduces eye strain.

The main functions of the explorer:
🦊 File Explorer Copy, move, rename, delete files and folders on your device.
🦊 Favorites Transfer your favorite documents to favorites.
🦊 File commander Easily manage your data, regardless of where it is located, in your device’s memory, microSD, SMB or FTP networks.
🦊 Functional to share Allows you to share files with friends, through social networks, instant messengers, etc.
